To edit the prompt, modify one of the themes in ./config/themes/shell/.
Note that changes will take effect immediately, without needing to restart the shell.
The built-in segments are in /usr/share/.../powerline/segments/{common,shell}.py.
Custom segments can be stored in a local directory using the paths setting in
config.json.

DOCS:
https://powerline.readthedocs.org/en/latest/configuration.html
https://powerline.readthedocs.org/en/latest/segments/common.html
